'''Ass''' (zh: Ñ ) is one of the most prized and versatile words in the [[American language]], possessing a whole host of meanings:

#A person's buttocks; a gathering of fat and muscle (mostly fat) upon which people sit.
#An "ass" is a type of hoofed mule that is notably lazy and stubborn, related to donkeys and horses. These are most commonly referred to as "those damn Mexicans".
#The buttocks of animals, the backside of an object, and an indeterminate location far away from one's present location are all referred to as the "ass end." Examples include "the ass end of that horse," "the ass end of my car" and "the ass end of town."
#An exciting new form of headgear.

