==The Ass in other languages==
The [[English]] add a completely superfluous "r" to the word, in honor of their long history of [[in_the_ass|ass piracy]]. Thus in their crazy moon-[[language]], ass is written [[YOU_ARE_DOING_IT_WRONG|"arse"]]. You should point out their mistake at every opportunity - it's the only way they'll learn.

